#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.82"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.82:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.82:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga "
msgstr "9. Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.82:0.3"
msgid "82. Gadrabhasutta "
msgstr "82. The Donkey "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.82:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gadrabho gogaṇaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti: "
msgstr "“Suppose, mendicants, a donkey followed behind a herd of cattle, thinking: "

#. VAR: ahampi dammo, ahampi dammo’ti → ahampamhā ahampamhāti (bj) | ahampi go amhā ahampi go amhāti (si) | ahampi amhā ahampi amhāti (s1-3, km, pts1) | ahampi go ahampi goti (?)
msgctxt "an3.82:1.2"
msgid "‘ahampi dammo, ahampi dammo’ti. "
msgstr "‘I can moo too! I can moo too!’ "

msgctxt "an3.82:1.3"
msgid "Tassa na tādiso vaṇṇo hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ, na tādiso saro hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ, na tādisaṃ padaṃ hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ. "
msgstr "But it doesn’t look like a cow, or sound like a cow, or leave a footprint like a cow. "

msgctxt "an3.82:1.4"
msgid "So gogaṇaṃyeva piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti: "
msgstr "Still it follows behind a herd of cattle, thinking: "

msgctxt "an3.82:1.5"
msgid "‘ahampi dammo, ahampi dammo’ti. "
msgstr "‘I can moo too! I can moo too!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.82:2.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu bhikkhusaṅghaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti: "
msgstr "In the same way, some mendicant follows behind the mendicant Saṅgha, thinking: "

msgctxt "an3.82:2.2"
msgid "‘ahampi bhikkhu, ahampi bhikkhū’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’m a monk too! I’m a monk too!’ "

msgctxt "an3.82:2.3"
msgid "Tassa na tādiso chando hoti adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, na tādiso chando hoti adhicittasikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, na tādiso chando hoti adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ. "
msgstr "But they don’t have the same enthusiasm for undertaking the training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom as the other mendicants. "

msgctxt "an3.82:2.4"
msgid "So bhikkhusaṅghaṃyeva piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti: "
msgstr "Still they follow behind the mendicant Saṇgha, thinking: "

msgctxt "an3.82:2.5"
msgid "‘ahampi bhikkhu, ahampi bhikkhū’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’m a monk too! I’m a monk too!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.82:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an3.82:3.2"
msgid "‘tibbo no chando bhavissati adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando bhavissati adhicittasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando bhavissati adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will have keen enthusiasm for undertaking the training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom.’ "

msgctxt "an3.82:3.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.82:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
